        <span class="icon">▼</span>
      </button>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <div class="accordion-inner">
          Each passenger is entitled to <strong>10 kg of luggage free of charge</strong>. Luggage is weighed at the terminal before boarding.
          <ul>
            <li>Extra weight: UGX 1,500 per kg above 10 kg</li>
            <li>Oversized items (bicycles, large boxes): UGX 15,000 flat rate</li>
            <li>All luggage must be securely packed and labeled with your name and destination</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
