      <div class="accordion-content">
        <div class="accordion-inner">
          The following items are <strong>strictly prohibited</strong> on all Link Bus vehicles and terminals:
          <ul>
            <li>Flammable liquids (petrol, diesel, kerosene)</li>
            <li>Explosives, fireworks, or ammunition</li>
            <li>Compressed gas cylinders (LPG, oxygen)</li>
            <li>Corrosive chemicals or acids</li>
            <li>Illegal narcotics or controlled substances</li>
            <li>Live animals (contact us for approved pet transport options)</li>
            <li>Any item exceeding 50 kg without prior terminal approval</li>
